": "Deemike", "created": 1777148225233, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DJT4MoreYears", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaMx9oj.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/x2eEPAxMDcxp.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/gK6MQAhJ3ZJOQZB0.jpeg", "width": 442, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UGC?DnNGkWIV01xZaK%M-VRjt7a}~VNGofV[", "full_resolution": [2295, 1320]}, "title": "The perfect blend of demonic evil and liberal retardation ", "last_comment_created": 1777148901967, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 14, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZaMuxpI", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 50, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8580188, "raw_content": "Key details:\n\n    The \"Gift\": Trump suggested the shipment contained sensitive, likely military-related materials sent by China despite earlier assurances, calling the content \"stuff\" that wasn't nice.\n    Intercepted Ship: The ship, identified in reports as the Touska, was intercepted by the U.S. Navy in the North Arabian Sea after ignoring warnings, with initial reports hinting at sensitive military components meant for Iran's missile program.\n    Context: The seizure occurred during a period of intense pressure on Iran, with Trump stating the move was a direct violation of previous assurances from Chinese President Xi Jinping regarding weapons shipments.\n    Response: While the U.S. highlighted the seizure, China\u2019s foreign ministry rejected the allegations as lacking a \"factual basis\" and accused the U.S. of interrupting normal trade. \n\nThe situation has created significant diplomatic tension, with Trump hinting that the incident is a form of \"war\" strategy", "author": "OrangeManNotBad", "created": 1777123325486, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DrumOctopus", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "President Trump stated that U.S. forces intercepted a ship carrying a \"top secret\" cargo from China to Iran, describing it as a \"gift\" that was \"not very nice\". The intercepted vessel, reportedly connected to military supplies, was seized in the North Arabian Sea, amid rising tensions over Iran tryi", "last_comment_created": 1777130263365, "content": "<p>Key details:</p>\n<pre><code>The &quot;Gift&quot;: Trump suggested the shipment contained sensitive, likely military-related materials sent by China despite earlier assurances, calling the content &quot;stuff&quot; that wasn't nice.\nIntercepted Ship: The ship, identified in reports as the Touska, was intercepted by the U.S. Navy in the North Arabian Sea after ignoring warnings, with initial reports hinting at sensitive military components meant for Iran's missile program.\nContext: The seizure occurred during a period of intense pressure on Iran, with Trump stating the move was a direct violation of previous assurances from Chinese President Xi Jinping regarding weapons shipments.\nResponse: While the U.S. highlighted the seizure, China\u2019s foreign ministry rejected the allegations as lacking a &quot;factual basis&quot; and accused the U.S. of interrupting normal trade. \n</code></pre>\n<p>The situation has created significant diplomatic tension, with Trump hinting that the incident is a form of &quot;war&quot; strategy</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 50, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaMwtEY", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 16, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8580892, "raw_content": "", "author": "ColonelKlink", "created": 1777146748189, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Live_free_or_die_55", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "edition.cnn.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaMwtEY.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://edition.cnn.com/2026/04/24/us/usf-students-missing-dead", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Why are they here in our country?", "last_comment_created": 1777148571963, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 16, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "After a University of South Florida doctoral student was found dead on a Tampa Bay bridge, his roommate has been charged with killing him and his friend \u2013 also a USF doctoral student \u2013 the sheriff\u2019s office said Saturday.", "large_image": "1vTyiVNioQOr9xnG.png", "title": "Roommate charged with